\n<p>A fast and slick theme framework built on the latest web techniques like HTML5, CSS3 and PHP 5.2+</p>\n\n<p><a class="button-more" href="http://www.yootheme.com/warp" target="_blank">Visit Website</a></p>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:36;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:13:"Warp Features";s:4:"text";s:285:"<p>All Warp features are available in this theme:</p>\n\n<ul class="check">\n	<li>Fast and Lightweight</li>\n	<li>Mobile Theme</li>\n	<li>Update Notifications</li>\n	<li>HTML5 markup</li>\n	<li>RTL Support</li>\n	<li>CSS Framework</li>\n	<li>Nice Admin UI</li>\n	<li>File Minification</li>\n</ul>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:37;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:18:"JavaScript Library";s:4:"text";s:170:"All client side effects use the JavaScript framework <a href="http://www.jquery.com" target="_blank">jQuery</a> which offers most reliable functionality and compact size!";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:38;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:13:"Icon Freebies";s:4:"text";s:893:"<ul class="line text-center">\n	<li>\n		<a href="http://www.yootheme.com/icons" target="_blank">\n			<figure>\n				<img class="size-auto" height="120" width="180" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/icons_socialbookmarks.png" alt="Social Bookmarks Icons">\n				<figcaption>Social Bookmarks Icons</figcaption>\n			</figure>\n		</a>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n		<a href="http://www.yootheme.com/icons" target="_blank">\n			<figure>\n				<img class="size-auto" height="120" width="180" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/icons_halloween.png" alt="Halloween Icons">\n				<figcaption>Halloween Icons</figcaption>\n			</figure>\n		</a>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n		<a href="http://www.yootheme.com/icons" target="_blank">\n			<figure>\n				<img class="size-auto" height="120" width="180" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/icons_html5geekmatt.png" alt="HTML5 Geek Icon">\n				<figcaption>HTML5 Geek Icon</figcaption>\n			</figure>\n		</a>\n	</li>\n</ul>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:39;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:13:"Icon Shipping";s:4:"text";s:305:"<a href="http://www.yootheme.com/icons" target="_blank" class="display-block text-center">\n	<figure class="remove-margin">\n		<img class="size-auto" height="120" width="180" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/icons_shipping.png" alt="Shipping Icons">\n		<figcaption>Shipping Icons</figcaption>\n	</figure>\n</a>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:40;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:16:"Icons E-Commerce";s:4:"text";s:310:"<a href="http://www.yootheme.com/icons" target="_blank" class="display-block text-center">\n	<figure class="remove-margin">\n		<img class="size-auto" height="120" width="180" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/icons_ecommerce.png" alt="E-Commerce Icons">\n		<figcaption>E-Commerce Icons</figcaption>\n	</figure>\n</a>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:41;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:12:"Icons Action";s:4:"text";s:300:"<a href="http://www.yootheme.com/icons" target="_blank" class="display-block text-center">\n	<figure class="remove-margin">\n		<img class="size-auto" height="120" width="180" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/icons_actions.png" alt="Action Icons">\n		<figcaption>Action Icons</figcaption>\n	</figure>\n</a>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:42;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:9:"Icons Box";s:4:"text";s:290:"<a href="http://www.yootheme.com/icons" target="_blank" class="display-block text-center">\n	<figure class="remove-margin">\n		<img class="size-auto" height="120" width="180" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/icons_box.png" alt="Box Icons">\n		<figcaption>Box Icons</figcaption>\n	</figure>\n</a>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:43;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:18:"Frontpage Headline";s:4:"text";s:158:"<div class="demoteaser text-center">\r\n	<h1 class="webfont-arvo">Beautiful. Useful. Simple.</h1>\r\n	<p>Get our latest Apps. Limited sale starts now!</p>\r\n</div>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:44;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:9:"App Store";s:4:"text";s:281:"<img style="margin: 0 15px 0 -20px; float: left;" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_icon_os.png" width="75" height="73">\r\n<div class="bfc-o">\r\n	<h3 class="module-title remove-margin">App Store</h3>\r\n	<p class="remove-margin-b">Available for iOS and Android devices.</p>\r\n</div>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:45;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:14:"Mobile Devices";s:4:"text";s:291:"<img style="margin: 0 15px 0 -20px; float: left;" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_icon_mobile.png" width="75" height="73">\r\n<div class="bfc-o">\r\n	<h3 class="module-title remove-margin">Mobile Devices</h3>\r\n	<p class="remove-margin-b">All Apps optimized for iPhone and iPad.</p>\r\n</div>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:46;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"Need a present?";s:4:"text";s:289:"<img style="margin: 0 15px 0 -20px; float: left;" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_icon_gift.png" width="75" height="73">\r\n<div class="bfc-o">\r\n	<h3 class="module-title remove-margin">Need a present?</h3>\r\n	<p class="remove-margin-b">Make your friends happy with our Apps.</p>\r\n</div>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:50;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:13:"Get Widgetkit";s:4:"text";s:549:"<a class="display-block text-center" href="http://www.yootheme.com/blog/item/root/introducing-widgetkit" target="_blank"><img class="size-auto" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/widgetkit_icon.png" alt="The next generation tool set for Joomla and WordPress" title="The next generation tool set for Joomla and WordPress" width="140" height="130" /></a>\r\n\r\n<p>The next generation tool set for Joomla and WordPress</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class="button-more" href="http://www.yootheme.com/blog/item/root/introducing-widgetkit" target="_blank">Visit Website</a></p>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:51;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:16:"Social Bookmarks";s:4:"text";s:259:"<div id="custombookmarks">\r\n	<h3>Want to stay informed? Follow us.</h3>\r\n	<div class="icons-social">\r\n		<a class="twitter" href="#"></a>\r\n		<a class="facebook" href="#"></a>\r\n		<a class="dribbble" href="#"></a>\r\n		<a class="rss" href="#"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:52;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:14:"Editors Choice";s:4:"text";s:390:"<p style="margin-top: 25px;" class="text-center">“These apps are well designed and easy to use. Its so great to get this high quality for this low price.”</p>\r\n<img class="align-center" width="92" height="11" alt="Rating" src="wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_rating.png" />\r\n<p class="text-center" style="font-size: 12px; font-style: italic;">Matt Aalhuis, <a href="#">App User</a></p>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:53;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:12:"Social Icons";s:4:"text";s:723:"<p><p>Shelf comes with four social Icons:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="icons-social">\r\n	<a class="twitter" href="#"></a>\r\n	<a class="facebook" href="#"></a>\r\n	<a class="dribbble" href="#"></a>\r\n	<a class="rss" href="#"></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>You can add them using the following code:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;icons-social&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;a class=&quot;twitter&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n	&lt;a class=&quot;facebook&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n	&lt;a class=&quot;dribbble&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n	&lt;a class=&quot;rss&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Possible class names are <strong>twitter, facebook, dribbble</strong> and <strong>rss</strong>.</p>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
