(107, 1, '2011-06-08 11:33:12', '2011-06-08 11:33:12', '<p>The Widgetkit Slideshow is the ultimate image and content slideshow for Joomla and WordPress. It''s flexible, easy to customize and completely build with HTML5 and CSS3. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Features</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="check">\r\n	<li>Clean and very lightweight code</li>\r\n	<li>15 eye-catching transition effects</li>\r\n	<li>Uses hardware accelerated CSS3 animations</li>\r\n	<li>JavaScript animation fallback for all Internet Explorers</li>\r\n	<li>Swipe navigation on mobile phones</li>\r\n	<li>Build with HTML5, CSS3, PHP 5.2+, and the latest jQuery version</li>\r\n	<li>Works with Joomla, WordPress and Stand-alone</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Example</h2>\r\n\r\n[widgetkit id=115]\r\n\r\n<h2>How To Use</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Widgetkit Slideshow takes full advantage of the very user-friendly Widgetkit administration user interface. It has never been easier to create and manage all the slideshows and their different slides in one place. After you created a slideshow you can load it anywhere in your theme using shortcodes or the universal Widgetkit Joomla module or WordPress widget.</p>', 'Slideshow', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '88-revision-2', '', '', '2011-06-08 11:33:12', '2011-06-08 11:33:12', '', 88, '@@SITE_URL@@/?p=107', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(501, 0, '2011-03-15 15:46:28', '2011-03-15 15:46:28', '{"type":"slideshow","id":22,"name":"Widgetkit Demo","settings":{"style":"default","autoplay":1,"interval":5000,"width":600,"height":300,"duration":500,"index":0,"navigation":1,"buttons":1,"slices":15,"animated":"randomFx","caption_animation_duration":500},"style":"default","items":{"4d7f89db79906":{"title":"Slide 1","content":"<a href=\\"#\\"><img src=\\"wp-content\\/uploads\\/yootheme\\/widgetkit\\/slideshow\\/image1.jpg\\" alt=\\"Image 01\\" height=\\"300\\" width=\\"600\\" \\/><\\/a>","caption":""},"4d7f89eab0e52":{"title":"Slide 2","content":"<a href=\\"#\\"><img src=\\"wp-content\\/uploads\\/yootheme\\/widgetkit\\/slideshow\\/image2.jpg\\" alt=\\"Image 02\\" height=\\"300\\" width=\\"600\\" \\/><\\/a>","caption":"This is a HTML caption with a <a href=\\"#\\">link<\\/a>."},"4d7f89f30cf9a":{"title":"Slide 3","content":"<a href=\\"#\\"><img src=\\"wp-content\\/uploads\\/yootheme\\/widgetkit\\/slideshow\\/image3.jpg\\" alt=\\"Image 03\\" height=\\"300\\" width=\\"600\\" \\/><\\/a>","caption":"This is another HTML caption with a <a href=\\"#\\">link<\\/a>."},"4d878180d9e3a":{"title":"Slide 4","content":"<a href=\\"#\\"><img src=\\"wp-content\\/uploads\\/yootheme\\/widgetkit\\/slideshow\\/image4.jpg\\" alt=\\"Image 04\\" height=\\"300\\" width=\\"600\\" \\/><\\/a>","caption":""},"4d87818847080":{"title":"Slide 5","content":"<a href=\\"#\\"><img src=\\"wp-content\\/uploads\\/yootheme\\/widgetkit\\/slideshow\\/image5.jpg\\" alt=\\"Image 05\\" height=\\"300\\" width=\\"600\\" \\/><\\/a>","caption":""}}}', 'Widgetkit Demo', 'default', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'test', '', '', '2011-06-08 16:18:55', '2011-06-08 16:18:55', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.50/Widgetkit/Website_WP/?p=22', 0, 'WIDGETKIT', 'slideshow', 0),
(110, 1, '2011-07-31 16:55:26', '2011-07-31 16:55:26', '<p>The Widgetkit Accordion enables you to display a set of items in a compact space, by clicking on each items header it expands or collapses it''s content section.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Features</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="check">\r\n	<li>Clean and very lightweight code</li>\r\n	<li>Smooth transitions on content section toggle</li>\r\n	<li>Option to match automatically the height of varying content</li>\r\n	<li>Option to auto collapse or allow multiple opened items</li>\r\n	<li>Built with HTML5, CSS3, PHP 5.2+, and the latest jQuery version</li>\r\n	<li>Works with Joomla, WordPress and Stand-alone</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Example</h2>\r\n\r\n[widgetkit id=503]\r\n\r\n<h2>How To Use</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Widgetkit Accordion lets you easily create and manage all the accordions contents through the user-friendly Widgetkit administration user interface. After you have created an accordion you can load it anywhere on your website using shortcodes or the universal Widgetkit Joomla module or WordPress widget.</p>', 'Accordion', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'accordion', '', '', '2011-07-31 17:07:23', '2011-07-31 17:07:23', '', 0, '@@SITE_URL@@/?page_id=110', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(109, 1, '2011-06-08 11:41:49', '2011-06-08 11:41:49', '<p>The Widgetkit Slideshow is the ultimate image and content slideshow for Joomla and WordPress. It''s flexible, easy to customize and completely build with HTML5 and CSS3. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Features</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="check">\r\n	<li>Clean and very lightweight code</li>\r\n	<li>15 eye-catching transition effects</li>\r\n	<li>Uses hardware accelerated CSS3 animations</li>\r\n	<li>JavaScript animation fallback for all Internet Explorers</li>\r\n	<li>Swipe navigation on mobile phones</li>\r\n	<li>Build with HTML5, CSS3, PHP 5.2+, and the latest jQuery version</li>\r\n	<li>Works with Joomla, WordPress and Stand-alone</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Example</h2>\r\n\r\n[widgetkit id=106]\r\n\r\n<h2>How To Use</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Widgetkit Slideshow takes full advantage of the very user-friendly Widgetkit administration user interface. It has never been easier to create and manage all the slideshows and their different slides in one place. After you created a slideshow you can load it anywhere in your theme using shortcodes or the universal Widgetkit Joomla module or WordPress widget.</p>', 'Slideshow', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '88-revision-3', '', '', '2011-06-08 11:41:49', '2011-06-08 11:41:49', '', 88, '@@SITE_URL@@/?p=109', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(111, 1, '2011-07-31 16:54:53', '2011-07-31 16:54:53', '<p>The Widgetkit Accordion enables you to display a set of items in a compact space, by clicking on each items header it expands or collapses it''s content section.</p>\n\n<h2>Features</h2>\n\n<ul class="check">\n	<li>Clean and very lightweight code</li>\n	<li>Smooth transitions on content section toggle</li>\n	<li>Option to match automatically the height of varying content</li>\n	<li>Option to auto collapse or allow multiple opened items</li>\n	<li>Built with HTML5, CSS3, PHP 5.2+, and the latest jQuery version</li>\n	<li>Works with Joomla, WordPress and Stand-alone</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Example</h2>\n\n[widgetkit id=151]\n\n<h2>How To Use</h2>\n\n<p>The Widgetkit Accordion lets you easily create and manage all the accordions contents through the user-friendly Widgetkit administration user interface. After you have created an accordion you can load it anywhere on your website using shortcodes or the universal Widgetkit Joomla module or WordPress widget.</p>', '', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '110-revision', '', '', '2011-07-31 16:54:53', '2011-07-31 16:54:53', '', 110, '@@SITE_URL@@/?p=111', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(112, 1, '2011-07-31 16:55:44', '2011-07-31 16:55:44', '<p>The Widgetkit Gallery provides a smart and automated way to publish images on your website. You only need to select the image folders and the whole gallery is generated automatically.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Features</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="check">\r\n	<li>Comes with image wall, slider and slideshow styles</li>\r\n	<li>Folder based image selection</li>\r\n	<li>Support for multiple image folders</li>\r\n	<li>Automatic thumbnail creation</li>\r\n	<li>Support for image captions and custom links</li>\r\n	<li>Uses the Widgetkit Spotlight and Lightbox</li>\r\n	<li>Built with HTML5, CSS3, PHP 5.2+, and the latest jQuery version</li>\r\n	<li>Works with Joomla, WordPress and Stand-alone</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Image Wall Example</h2>\r\n<p>This is an image wall with zoom effect, no margins and squared corners using the lightbox.</p>\r\n[widgetkit id=504]\r\n\r\n<h2>Polaroid Example</h2>\r\n<p>This is an image wall with scattered polaroid pictures using the lightbox.</p>\r\n[widgetkit id=506]\r\n\r\n<h2>Slider Example 1</h2>\r\n<p>This is an image slider where the image centers automatically during the effect. It also features a spotlight caption and the lightbox.</p>\r\n[widgetkit id=508]\r\n\r\n<h2>Slider Example 2</h2>\r\n<p>This is an image slider where the image stays left during the effect.</p>\r\n[widgetkit id=507]\r\n\r\n<h2>Slideshow Example</h2>\r\n<p>This is an image gallery using all the features from the slideshow widget.</p>\r\n[widgetkit id=502]\r\n\r\n<h2>Spotlight Example</h2>\r\n<p>This is an image wall with some margins and rounded corners using the spotlight and lightbox.</p>\r\n[widgetkit id=505]\r\n\r\n<h2>How To Use</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Widgetkit Gallery comes with a user-friendly administration user interface which let''s you create new galleries with just a few clicks. The integrated directory browser let''s you easily add or remove source directories of your images. All galleries can be loaded anywhere in your theme using shortcodes or the universal Widgetkit Joomla module or WordPress widget.</p>', 'Gallery', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gallery', '', '', '2011-07-31 17:08:48', '2011-07-31 17:08:48', '', 0, '@@SITE_URL@@/?page_id=112', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(113, 1, '2011-07-31 16:55:43', '2011-07-31 16:55:43', '<p>The Widgetkit Gallery provides a smart and automated way to publish images on your website. You only need to select the image folders and the whole gallery is generated automatically.</p>\n\n<h2>Features</h2>\n\n<ul class="check">\n	<li>Comes with image wall, slider and slideshow styles</li>\n	<li>Folder based image selection</li>\n	<li>Support for multiple image folders</li>\n	<li>Automatic thumbnail creation</li>\n	<li>Support for image captions and custom links</li>\n	<li>Uses the Widgetkit Spotlight and Lightbox</li>\n	<li>Built with HTML5, CSS3, PHP 5.2+, and the latest jQuery version</li>\n	<li>Works with Joomla, WordPress and Stand-alone</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Image Wall Example</h2>\n<p>This is an image wall with zoom effect, no margins and squared corners using the lightbox.</p>\n[widgetkit id=153]\n\n<h2>Polaroid Example</h2>\n<p>This is an image wall with scattered polaroid pictures using the lightbox.</p>\n[widgetkit id=155]\n\n<h2>Slider Example 1</h2>\n<p>This is an image slider where the image centers automatically during the effect. It also features a spotlight caption and the lightbox.</p>\n[widgetkit id=157]\n\n<h2>Slider Example 2</h2>\n<p>This is an image slider where the image stays left during the effect.</p>\n[widgetkit id=156]\n\n<h2>Slideshow Example</h2>\n<p>This is an image gallery using all the features from the slideshow widget.</p>\n[widgetkit id=118]\n\n<h2>Spotlight Example</h2>\n<p>This is an image wall with some margins and rounded corners using the spotlight and lightbox.</p>\n[widgetkit id=154]\n\n<h2>How To Use</h2>\n\n<p>The Widgetkit Gallery comes with a user-friendly administration user interface which let''s you create new galleries with just a few clicks. The integrated directory browser let''s you easily add or remove source directories of your images. All galleries can be loaded anywhere in your theme using shortcodes or the universal Widgetkit Joomla module or WordPress widget.</p>', 'Gallery', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '112-revision', '', '', '2011-07-31 16:55:43', '2011-07-31 16:55:43', '', 112, '@@SITE_URL@@/?p=113', 0, 'revision', '', 0);

